"after a product is installed on-site, use the <b>Repair app</b>. By "
"selecting the specific product, you can accurately add or remove components, "
"ensuring your records reflect the true \"as-built\" configuration."
msgstr ""
"設置や整備・保守の際、破損した部品や適合しない部品の交換が必要になる場合があ"
