msgstr ""
"当社は、カスタマイズされたソリューションを提供し、お客様一人ひとりのニーズに"
"合わせた最高水準のサービスをお届けします。"

#. module: custom_industrial_equipment
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_industrial_equipment.contactus
msgid ""
"We provide 24/7 support through various channels, including live chat, "
"email, and phone, to assist with any queries."
msgstr ""
"ライブチャット、Eメール、電話など、さまざまなチャネルを通じて24時間365日サ"
"ポートを提供し、あらゆるお問い合わせに対応いたします。"

#. module: custom_industrial_equipment
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_industrial_equipment.homepage
msgid ""
"We provide a 30-day satisfaction guarantee for all custom orders. Items must "
"be in their original condition, unused, and include the order confirmation. "
"Refunds are processed within 5-7 business days after receiving the returned "
"item."
msgstr ""
"当社では、すべてのカスタムオーダに対して30日間の満足保証を提供しています。返"
"品対象のプロダクトは、未使用で、元の状態のまま、かつオーダ確認書を同梱してい"
"る必要があります。返金は、返品商品を受領後、5～7営業日以内に処理されます。"

#. module: custom_industrial_equipment
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_industrial_equipment.homepage
msgid ""
"We’re dedicated to delivering timely and effective manufacturing solutions "
"to ensure your success."
msgstr ""
"私たちは、お客様の成功を確実にするため、タイムリーかつ効果的な製造ソリュー"
"ションの提供に尽力しています。"

#. module: custom_industrial_equipment
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_industrial_equipment.welcome_article_body
msgid "When you're ready to manage a transfer:"
msgstr "転送を管理する準備が整ったら："

#. module: custom_industrial_equipment
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_industrial_equipment.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"When you're ready, you have the flexibility to create an invoice for either "
"a full or a partial payment, such as a down payment. All invoices generated "
"are tracked and can be managed through the <b>Invoices app</b>."
msgstr ""
"準備が整ったら、全額支払いだけでなく前受金などの一部支払いについても請求書を"
"作成できます。作成された請求書はすべて記録され、<b>請求書アプリ</b> から管理"
"できます。"

#. module: custom_industrial_equipment
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_industrial_equipment.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"While you can manually move an operation with a simple drag and drop, keep "
"in mind this change is isolated to that specific work order and will not re-"
"plan the others."
msgstr ""
"操作はドラッグ&ドロップで手動移動できますが、この変更はその特定の作業オーダに"
"限定され、他の作業オーダの再計画は行われない点にご注意ください。"

#. module: custom_industrial_equipment
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_industrial_equipment.homepage
msgid ""
"With over 15 years of industry expertise, we deliver tailored solutions and "
"strategic insights for your conveyor manufacturing needs."
msgstr ""
